SubjectOrder directing Export Development Canada to lend monies to General Dynamics Land Systems-Canada
PrecisOrder directing Export Development Canada (1) to lend monies to GENERAL DYNAMICS LAND SYSTEMS-CANADA (GDLS-C) in accordance with any authorizations obtained from the Minister for International Trade pursuant to section 23 of the Export Development Act; and (2) do all such ancillary or other things as may be required or advisable to give effect to this directive.
